about.summary: Python interface to Graphviz's Dot language

name: pydotplus
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.0.2" %}

package:
  name: pydotplus
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pydotplus-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pydotplus/pydotplus-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 0e2fc3dbdfd846819d4cd3769cb4595b

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pyparsing >=2.0.1

  run:
    - python
    - pyparsing >=2.0.1

test:
  imports:
    - pydotplus

about:
  home: http://pydotplus.readthedocs.org/
  license: MIT
  summary: "Python interface to Graphviz's Dot language"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - chrisfilo
    - satra
